tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE telehealth_analytics (
    user_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    login_time TIMESTAMP,
    duration_minutes INT,
    device_type VARCHAR(50),
    user_location VARCHAR(100),
    connection_speed VARCHAR(20),
    call_quality_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS appointments (
  appointment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  doctor_id UUID,
  appointment_date DATE,
  appointment_time TIME,
  consultation_fee DECIMAL,
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS rating_reviews (
  review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  appointment_id UUID,
  user_id UUID,
  doctor_id UUID,
  rating INT,
  review_text TEXT,
);

CREATE TABLE telehealth_users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    date_joined DATE
);

CREATE TABLE telehealth_appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    appointment_date DATE,
    doctor_name VARCHAR(255),
    appointment_type VARCHAR(50),
    consultation_fee DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES telehealth_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE telehealth_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES telehealth_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Telehealth_Provider (
  provider_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_name VARCHAR(255),
  provider_specialty VARCHAR(255),
  provider_location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE Telehealth_Patient (
  patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  patient_age INT,
  patient_gender VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE Telehealth_Appointment (
  appointment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id UUID,
  patient_id UUID,
  appointment_date DATE,
  appointment_time TIME
)

CREATE TABLE Telehealth_Metrics (
  metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_id UUID,
  patient_id UUID,
  metric_name VARCHAR(255),
  metric_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Procedure (
    procedure_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    procedure_name VARCHAR(255),
    procedure_category VARCHAR(255),
    provider_id INT,
    date_performed DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Patient (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    date_of_birth DATE,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Provider (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(255),
    specialization VARCHAR(50),
    address VARCHAR(255),
    contact_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE Appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    provider_id INT,
    appointment_date DATETIME,
    appointment_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date_recorded DATE,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value DECIMAL(10, 2),
    provider_id INT
);
